<title>ạ̹nt ạlmạlk ạlwḥyd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạ̹nt ạlmạlk ạlwḥyd .. ạ̹ʿlạn mlkk lynạ yzyd
 wʿly̱ ḥsạb dm ạlṣlyb .. ʿly̱ ạ̹blys ạlnṣr ạ̉kyd)2
 ạlqrạr- (bạlhtạfạt wạltsbyḥạt .. dạkẖlyn ḥrwbnạ mntṣryn
 wbạ̉gẖnyạt rạfʿyn rạyạt .. rạyạt ạlnṣrẗ byk gẖạlbyn)2
 2- (nrfʿ ạsmk yạ ạbn ạllh .. dạ bslṭạnk lynạ ḥyạẗ
 tḥny̱ lạsmk kl jbạh .. tsbyḥk mn kl sẖfạh)2
 3- (lyk ạlqwẗ wạlslṭạn .. lyk bndẖyʿ kl ạlạ̉lḥạn
 wbrwḥk nrfʿ ạ̉ngẖạm .. ạsmk yʿly̱ fy kl mkạn)2</lyrics>
</song>